OL,5,Cviolence rises
OL,7,FIn the latest of a series of reports
OL,8,Finto how violence is impacting young
OL,9,Fpeople, ITV News has been given
OL,10,Fexclusive access to a classroom
OL,11,Flockdown rehearsal.
OL,13,FArchbishop Ilsley Catholic School in
OL,14,Fthe Acocks Green area of Birmingham
OL,15,Fallowed cameras in to film the
OL,16,Fpractice, which is becoming widespread
OL,17,Fnationally.
