OL,7,FIt sees children hide under desks,
OL,8,Flock windows and barricade doors in
OL,9,Fthe event of intruders or serious
OL,10,Fincidents like weapons being reported
OL,11,Fin school.
OL,13,FDan Corrigan, the school's assistant
OL,14,Fheadteacher and safeguarding lead, was
OL,15,Famong the first to formulate a plan
OL,16,Fseven years ago but says they are now
OL,17,Fessential to security.
