OL,7,FHe said: "I would worry about
OL,8,Finvestment in schools generally, and
OL,9,Fanything we can get to make sure that
OL,10,Fschools are able to prioritise safety
OL,11,Fand security - I know school leaders
OL,12,Fwould want that, first and foremost,
OL,13,Fright now."
OL,15,FIt comes amid rising concerns around
OL,16,Fviolence involving young people.
