OL,7,FThere were more than 3,200 knife or
OL,8,Fweapons offences committed by children
OL,9,Fthat resulted in a caution or sentence
OL,10,Fin the year to March 2024, according
OL,11,Fto the Youth Justice Board for England.
OL,13,FThe statistics are lower than the
OL,14,Fprevious year but a fifth higher than
OL,15,Fin 2014.
