OL,7,FThe legislation, which is named in
OL,8,Fhonour of Martyn Hett, who was killed
OL,9,Fin the Manchester Arena terror attack
OL,10,Fin 2017, requires settings including
OL,11,Fschools to consider how they would
OL,12,Frespond to extreme events like terror
OL,13,Fattacks.
OL,15,FIt became law in April last year but
OL,16,Fwill not come into force formally
OL,17,Funtil the end of a two-year
OL,18,F"implementation period".
